{"tid":1676694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【高質反送中歌曲】一起走 go with me","createTime":"2019-10-26T15:22:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T07:17:02.000Z","uid":118767,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7d5552d78b1143af515fe6c09d8fdf99cb082884","tid":1676694,"uid":118767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T15:22:40.000Z","msg":"喺youtube搵搵吓見到，真心好聽，旋律又易記，咁都只係得千幾個views，冇天理。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好淨係唱死榮光同肥媽，俾下機會其它革命歌，學多一兩首傍身，唔好浪費手足嘅心血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UNBSZUfHZ_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUNBSZUfHZ_0&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjg1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=9bf0b7cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UNBSZUfHZ_0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歌詞：<br />\n<br />\n牽你手 走上街中 共你漫遊 Hand in hand, dreaming with you<br />\n這個夏日 淚水 汗水 在流  This summer, full of tears and sweat <br />\n下決心  留到最後  With determination<br />\n那管痛楚內心爭鬥  No matter how much pain and conflict we had<br />\n沉默 難以修補缺口  Silence didn&rsquo;t heal our wounds<br />\n<br />\n花已開 鋪滿街巷 遍地漫延  Blossoms everywhere, filling every street<br />\n這個夏日 為理想 走上最前  This summer, chasing our dream<br />\n記著善良 懷著信念  With kindness and belief<br />\n守護彼此  互信牽引  We guard each other with trust<br />\n同路陌生變最親  On the way, strangers become comrades<br />\n<br />\n結伴遊走. 請珍惜這份自由  Go with me  treasure our freedom<br />\n伴我飛 創造更光明宇宙  Fly with me, create a better world<br />\n攜手 淌血流淚 誓要桿衛  Holding hands, defend with tears and blood<br />\n護我家園 和勇互守  Protect our home, backing each other up<br />\n<br />\n如水  不怕風雨 共你聚頭  Be water  gather and fear no pain <br />\n願我們謹記約定那天相認一剎  Remember the promise that we&rsquo;ll meet again<br />\n作暖流 憑自信 懷著愛 無懼怕  勇敢一起  奮鬥  Stay warm, with faith, love and bravery<br />\n<br />\n遊走  請珍惜這份自由   Go, treasure our freedom<br />\n飛  創造更光明宇宙  Fly, create a better world<br />\n攜手  淌血流淚 誓要桿衛  Holding hands, with blood and tears, we must protect<br />\n護我家園 高呼和應   Protect our home, respond to the calling<br />\n<br />\n如火  不休止 散發熱情  Be fire, restless passion<br />\n到那日擺脫隔膜  慶祝公義得勝  One day we&rsquo;ll celebrate our victory for justice closely together<br />\n為我城  憑自信 懷著愛 齊建設 美好風景  Build a better city, with faith and love <br />\n共你見證  We will witness"},{"pid":"d6f13eb4c028a8ba262d82fc94e866ff0b90b808","tid":1676694,"uid":274538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T15:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UiED4J5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUiED4J5.jpg&h=56a89dd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vb1OHvN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvb1OHvN.gif&h=b89118e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4bc68dba707c239f81143df0772802eb9f79371f","tid":1676694,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T15:23:35.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好剩係懲罰出名嘅黃店？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675556</a>"},{"pid":"2a7e9f6dfbb3833506ea9ad198b47ed8eaea641a","tid":1676694,"uid":118767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T15:23:58.000Z","msg":"自推1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483fd5af81286f138878637d64550870655d5a63","tid":1676694,"uid":118767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T15:24:16.000Z","msg":"自推2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67646affa762f8833db80c685e4cb9e156e6e405","tid":1676694,"uid":30767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T15:25:15.000Z","msg":"【行動post】聽日3點尖沙咀見！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1676687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1676687</a>"},{"pid":"880fe22049b3afd4e546e4050e89058ddcaac5f1","tid":1676694,"uid":118767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c